quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  12,43,"Inna ugellid: \"nek wala$ ûa testan tiqebwaniyin, la tent teppent ûa tuvâifin, akked ûa tyedrin tizegzawin, tiyav d tiqquôanin. A yimvebbôen, ssefrut iyi d targit, ma tellam seg wid issefruyen tirga"
  12,44,"Nnan: \"d tirga iwlellsen. Ur nelli d imusnawen i usefru n tirga"
  12,45,"Win i isellken si sin nni, armi tallit id immekti, inna: \"nek, ad awen d awi$ asefru ines, aznet iyi"
  12,46,"A Yusef, bab n tidep, ssefru ya$ d: ûa testan tiqebwaniyin, la tent teppent ûa tuvâifin, akked ûa tyedrin tizegzawin, tiyav d tiqquôanin. Amar, ma u$ale$ ar imdanen, amar ad éôen"
  12,47,"Inna: \"zerâat ûa iseggwasen imyevfaôen. Ayen tzerâam, eooet ep di tyedrin is, siwa cwiî ara teççem"
  12,48,"Sinna, deffir sen, a d asen ûa iwaâôen. Ad ççen ayen i sen theggam siwa cwiî, seg wayen txeznem"
  12,49,"Sinna a d ias, deffir waya, useggwas n tallalt i medden, ideg ara éden"